data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom pool home in the desirable Ridgemoore community with curb appeal to spare! Its all in the living space as the home features an open floor plans throughout, high ceilings, and plenty of natural light. The lanai to the rear of the property is big enough for any backyard barbecue overlooking the pool with an impressive L-shaped backyard in the backyard. Let's not forget the ample parking space with a 2 car garage and a looooong driveway with enough space for 4-6 more vehicles! The corner lot front yard is enough for any large/growing family with plenty of running room for the kiddies! HOA fees couldn't be lower, don’t miss this opportunity to own this amazing home in a prime location. Age of roof unknown, buyer to rely on inspection report for all repairs needed. Schedule your showing today!
